I am so excited... Today has been one awesome day...

I got my tickets for The Big Wu Family Reunion. It's the weekend of my birthday in Geneva, Minnesota. I am soo pumped. Between that and Bonnaroo, I'm gunna have one hell of a summer.

Anyways, I'm going on a "date" with Ryan tonight. Oo lala. Ryan Ryan Ryan. Haha. I don't know what it is about him, but I can't stop thinking about him. Weird.... Anyways, we're gunna go out to dinner and then go see "Secret Window". Sounds like a gay ol' time to me...

So last night I stopped by Mike M's house to get a satchel... And he said something to me that I was somewhat confused about. Because I don't know in what terms he meant it. Maybe one of you can help me figure it out.... He said "hey, give me a call sometime"... So, I'm wondering if he meant it like "hey, keep giving me a call for herb"... or "hey, call me and lets hang out".... Hmmm, don't know.

Well, that is all... Good day to you.

Wow guys. It's been a while since I wrote in this thing. I don't even think anyone reads this... But if they do, then cool.

Today was boring, I had school all day. After school I smoked a pipe with Adrian (LOL!)... And then I went and played Risk with Kitt and Ian. And then I swung by Ryan's for a little. What a day... Heh, right.

The more I hang with him the more I am beginning to like Ryan. He is fucking cool, and I can just sit around and talk to him for hours. We have tons of shit in common. I think I really like the fact that he hasn't even attempted to get with me in any way whatsoever. so yeah, I like Ryan. Oo lala.
I am falling back into love with the same person that caused me the most happiness, but yet the most pain of anyone I have ever met.... WHAT DO I DO!?!?!

Hmm... NIU was hella fun. It probably would have been more fun if I was drinking along with everybody else. But, eh, fuck that. It was still tons of fun though.

I don't really have any thing else to say. Except that it's amazing how much you realize you like someone after you think you are over them. (Hint, its just because you don't see them that you think you are over them!) But, trust me... I am definetly not over Matt. LoL. 

Well, I'm gunna go to sleep, I'm exhausted! Later!

Well, what is new...
1)Me and Mikey broke up because he's a dumbass.
2)I hung out with Matt last night. It was awkward, but actually quite fun. We sat around and talked for 4 hours. I don't really know whats going on with that.... But, it makes me happy to know at least he doesn't hate me...

So, I dropped my car off at 9:00 this morning to have the fuel leak looked at... I called at 3:00 this afternoon to get progress on it because I need to know whether or not I need to get a rental car so I have a way to get to school tomorrow. Here is the conversation I had with the dumb car guy...

Car Guy: "I'm sorry, we haven't gotten a chance to look at it yet."
Me: "Not to be rude, but I dropped it off 6 hours ago and you're telling me you haven't even taken five minutes to LOOK at it yet?"
Car Guy: "Well ma'am, we're very busy. I'm sorry."
Me: "I understand that you are busy, but you told me if I dropped it off by 9 this morning that you would be able to look at it immediately and give me a call back"
Car Guy: "We're moving as fast as we can"
Me: "Last time I took my car here you guys did this same thing. Your service is horrible, I'm done talking to you... I will have my dad call you back."
-=And then I hung up=-

Hah, let my dad deal with the bastards!!

Geez... It's gunna take me around 3 weeks to have my beautiful truck back. *Tear*. Because the fuel line is popped so I have a gas leak, so I have to go get that fixed at the dealership... And then take it elsewhere to get the body work done from that stupid bitch that hit me. God damnit! ACK!

God damn it, people piss me off. I was just simply cutting through a parking lot on my way to get cigarettes, not doing anything wrong. When this lady going the opposite way of me runs the stop sign, sideswipes the mustang that was just coming off of Randall Road, and then the lady's car went flying straight into mine. That fucking pisses me off. My car is not even 3 months old, and the whole front end is going to have to be replaced. It looks like shit, ahhh! God I am so pissed about that! And it definitely wrecked my night last night. And my back is fucking killing me... But, hooray for vicodin!

Good morning guys. What's goin on? I'm just hangin out not doing a whole lot of anything. Granted it is 8:00 in the morning, so that probably has something to do with it! 

Tonight I am going to test my Simpsons trivia for a change to win a Simpsons bowling ball. In which I will give it to my brother because he (along with Dan and Bob) are going to join a bowling league with me this summer. That should be fun. We are going to suck, but thats ok, I don't care about winning. I am just happy that I found some people who will actually join a league with me.

Well, Bonnaroo is getting closer and closer. And I am so excited already! It will be fuckin awesome! Yesssss.

Last night I won 5 dollars playing pool. That was cool. I kicked Roberts ass 5 times in a row. A dollar a game. Woo Woo for that.

Well, I should probably take a shower and get ready for a beautiful day. I can't wait for Summer weather!! Later!

Hey everybody! This is my first entry on this thing. Woo Woo for that. I suppose I will start off by saying a little about myself... I'm Mandey, I'm 18, and I drive a Red Ford Ranger. I am a freshman at MCC and I am planning to major in journalism. I have a really cool boyfriend whose name is Mike. But I call him Mikey. Haha. He's super:-)

So, on to what is going on... Well,  my best friend, Kitt, has been trying to get into the Navy for a while now. He told me that he stopped doing any drugs and that he was guarenteed to get in. He went down yesterday and failed his drug test for Coke, Ecstasy, and Pot. I was pissed cuz he told me that he didn't do drugs!! Then, his recruiter gave him a break, let him drink a detox drink, and he took the drug test again. This time he passed, so of yesterday he was able to make it into the navy. All that was left to do was go down this morning and talk to the Commanding Officer. He went and did that, and the C.O. told him that he can't be in the Navy. Kitt told me that it was because of his police records, but to my understanding as long as you don't have any felonies... then you will be fine to get in. Kitt doesn't have any felonies, so I am thinking it has to do with the failing drug test. I am pissed at him now because this is the second time he went through all this shit, the second time he lied to me about it, and the second time he will not be accepted. He is a good friend of mine, and I care about him... But I have very little sympathy for him because if he wants to get into the Navy and make something of his life, then he has to stop doing drugs. And I guess he isn't ready to do that yet... So yeah, I'm pissed.

Sorry, I had to vent! But for now I need to go smoke a cigarette. Later!!
